(42, 14, 14, 27, 12, 2, 3, 'recompensed at the resurrection', 'Resurrection and Reward Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of resurrection and the rewards associated with it. Both passages speak of a future awakening and recompense for the just, emphasizing the outcomes of righteousness.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
