(42, 14, 15, 42, 13, 29, 29, 'kingdom of God', 'Connection of the Kingdom of God', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of sitting in the kingdom of God. The SOURCE verse mentions eating bread in the kingdom, while the TARGET passage refers to sitting down in the kingdom, highlighting the communal aspect of this experience.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
