(42, 14, 16, 20, 9, 1, 2, 'great supper', 'Invitation to a Feast', 'This connection highlights the theme of a great feast in both passages. In Luke, a man invites many to a supper, while in Proverbs, Wisdom prepares a table and invites others to partake.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
