(42, 14, 17, 40, 10, 1, 4, 'Come; for all things are now ready', 'Invitation and Empowerment', 'This connection highlights the theme of invitation and readiness in both passages. In Luke, the servant invites those bidden to come, while in Matthew, Jesus empowers his disciples to go forth and heal, suggesting a readiness to act.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
