(42, 14, 17, 42, 3, 4, 6, 'Come; for all things are now ready', 'Invitation and Preparation for Salvation', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparation for God''s invitation to salvation. Both passages emphasize the readiness of God''s plan, with the servant calling others to come and the voice in the wilderness preparing the way for the Lord.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
